{"tid":2461483,"cid":7,"subCid":0,"title":"一句講晒，張蔓莎定張蔓姿?","createTime":"2021-03-25T12:13:01.000Z","updateTime":"2021-03-25T13:53:20.000Z","uid":58335,"like":125,"dislike":32,"uniUserReply":52,"replies":[{"pid":"4c932dff48b99cce199a32922a266a0d566c9d47","tid":2461483,"uid":58335,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-03-25T12:13:01.000Z","msg":"張蔓莎<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/good.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n張蔓姿<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dislike.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n兩姐妹都係知性美<br />\n係真文青<br />\n又識唱歌<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n又識做戲<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n又識彈琴<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n又會睇文學書<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n樣唔洗講<br />\n係特別靚<br />\n呀妹笑起上黎世界都溶化了<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/love.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/love.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n家姐Cool到世界冰冷了<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/love.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/love.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n真係諗唔到世界上仲有邊個人有佢兩姐妹咁完美<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n我好似戀愛了<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/love.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/love.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n準備4月5號睇YOLO的練習曲瘋狂睇牙姿<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/bomb.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/bomb.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n張蔓莎<br />\n<img src=\"https://img.mnmulu.com/upload/2019/10/18/zhangmansuo1037125.jpg.@ERESIZE@.mw_1000,qt_80.9c3e75.jpg.webp\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.mnmulu.com%2Fupload%2F2019%2F10%2F18%2Fzhangmansuo1037125.jpg.%40ERESIZE%40.mw_1000%2Cqt_80.9c3e75.jpg.webp&h=f3916f17&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://encrypted-tbn0.gstatic.com/images?q=tbn:ANd9GcSOs7qaO-BpAz5wbt2boCTLcmACYCR3XlENDg&amp;usqp=CAU\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fencrypted-tbn0.gstatic.com%2Fimages%3Fq%3Dtbn%3AANd9GcSOs7qaO-BpAz5wbt2boCTLcmACYCR3XlENDg%26usqp%3DCAU&h=f9b757e3&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://p1.meituan.net/movie/9d7a73c5dc325f60939cc3eecc97c86050300.jpg@80q\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fp1.meituan.net%2Fmovie%2F9d7a73c5dc325f60939cc3eecc97c86050300.jpg%4080q&h=ce4c4e77&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://img.appledaily.com.tw/campaign/44/6a00606abcd1c30507a08b4e9370644d.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.appledaily.com.tw%2Fcampaign%2F44%2F6a00606abcd1c30507a08b4e9370644d.jpg&h=edd4db4f&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://img.mnmulu.com/upload/2019/10/18/zhangmansuo1037128.jpg.@ERESIZE@.mw_1000,qt_80.9c3e75.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.mnmulu.com%2Fupload%2F2019%2F10%2F18%2Fzhangmansuo1037128.jpg.%40ERESIZE%40.mw_1000%2Cqt_80.9c3e75.jpg&h=8edcef5c&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n張蔓姿<br />\n<img src=\"https://static02-proxy.hket.com/res/v3/image/content/2770000/2770075/20201006cheung4_1024.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fstatic02-proxy.hket.com%2Fres%2Fv3%2Fimage%2Fcontent%2F2770000%2F2770075%2F20201006cheung4_1024.jpg&h=fa81b88f&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://www.harpersbazaar.com.hk/var/harpersbazaarhk/storage/images/celebrity/interview/gigi-cheung/6/1348657-3-chi-HK/6_img_708_h.jpg\" data-thumbnail-s